"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-weird-1929738-olympic-village-hinge-dating-apps\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  A woman has been praised for her \\\"genius\\\" dating app hack, which has apparently led to her matching with an Olympic gold medallist.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sofia, known onTikTokas @sofiaelizabethshackup, revealed how she tweaked her Hinge settings to the Olympic Village and ended up chatting with a victor from the US.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hinge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.695958575396905e-19, \"text\": \"Hinge\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hinge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hinge\"}, {\"begin\": 234, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999990649518902, \"rank\": 9.350378165684753e-07, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.988339240262538, \"rank\": 0.011377064542668864, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her video, she gushed: \\\"Whoever said to change your location to the 'Olympic Village' currently in Paris to match with an Olympian, I just want to thank you from the bottom of my heart for adding to the 'lore' that I will tell my future children about.\\\"\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999783303795, \"rank\": 2.1669657400086604e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999499392352191, \"rank\": 4.7724154240822885e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She claimed to have \\\"instantly kicked it off\\\" with the athlete, adding while failing to contain her laughter: \\\"We get to talking and honestly, I could feel the chemistry and the future gold medal in my hands.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When it was their time to shine in their sport, they did not just shine, they won.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They won the first gold medal for the United States of America - that's my match baby, that's my match.\\\"\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \":People gobsmacked to learn what .com stands for after 39 years  :'I took revenge on my neighbours who keep using my driveway - it made it worse'  :Olympic surfer rescued from drowning by brave lifeguards during dangerous storm  Despite not having spoken since, Sofia remains proud of her dating strategy.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofia\", \"score\": 0.9999578742302795, \"rank\": 4.211498803747081e-05, \"text\": \"Sofia\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained that she simply adjusted her Hinge location settings to Saint-Ouen, Paris, where the Olympic Village is located.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hinge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.695958575396905e-19, \"text\": 